{"tid":1900332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部新發言人上任第二天 被發現Twitter追蹤蒼井空","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T03:31:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c63006a6e912195992e976c3058f4f6e30e3821","tid":1900332,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8lKdXLf5V97at4iBeJmGmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/a2evbGLAcAan2nmivPYOgg--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/f05816da87c9c5b8648a9602f9ca8d15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8lKdXLf5V97at4iBeJmGmA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fa2evbGLAcAan2nmivPYOgg--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Ff05816da87c9c5b8648a9602f9ca8d15&h=1505248c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國外交部新任發言人趙立堅（圖），被網友發現推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空。（翻攝自@zlj517推特）<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部近來風波不斷，先是發言人華春瑩被發現翻牆給「習近平下台」的貼文按讚，如今又傳出新任發言人趙立堅推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空，再度引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅推特帳號成立將近9年，擁有25萬粉絲追蹤，由於他經常透過推特回應中國議題，有著「網紅發言人」「戰狼外交官」的稱號。本月24日，趙立堅以新任發言人的身分首度在例行記者會亮相，由華春瑩親自介紹給媒體。<br />\n<br />\n但趙立堅上任第二天，就被網友發現其推特帳號追蹤了日本前AV女優蒼井空。儘管目前趙立堅已取消追蹤，但截圖持續網路上被瘋傳。截至目前為止，中國官方或趙立堅本人都未針對此事做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部新任發言人趙立堅，被網友發現推特帳號追蹤日本知名前AV女優蒼井空。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國大陸網友紛紛表示「小趙本色演出！」「蒼井空是世界的！」「中國外交部真是人才濟濟」「能不能不要那麼露骨，改名援交部比較合理。」"},{"pid":"f4e2bf3b6dcf1a2c8f6a46e5d1a6acb0b0943f8a","tid":1900332,"uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrL2d2B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrL2d2B.jpg&h=daa25985&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90befb2357a5d45bd110d0406100d591e11c6b61","tid":1900332,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3013ee3d0cd60f32813833e7bbc3f86fcf46e6","tid":1900332,"uid":225798,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"大家都是男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8855a206c746abd4ef2bff18466963a349fea557","tid":1900332,"uid":39796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"有著「淫狼外交官」的稱號"},{"pid":"c31ac70fc357a296458573b31dc98171f7396077","tid":1900332,"uid":239853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"「能不能不要那麼露骨，改名援交部比較合理。」<br />\n以後唔叫口交部都可以叫援交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e1910f7a38cc8313f0e2572772deddbe817eba","tid":1900332,"uid":309553,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GuFLaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GuFLaW.jpg&h=cd910e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccff51ed4675ac8fa7a6aa3f231f9d50e78023cc","tid":1900332,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c5126de07a554fe7650862ab77e9b0bbcd3af3","tid":1900332,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"良家婦女嚟，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333b1b168f142d95c3a6a101476e4f896e22bae2","tid":1900332,"uid":13818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT